{"tid":1735190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[關公] Poly入面負傷既手足快啲一齊拍條求救片, 中英文都要有!!","createTime":"2019-11-18T13:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T14:48:06.000Z","uid":264624,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2a24a9e7a02a6bc01efad8533458ecb91d0eaa7a","tid":1735190,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"所有人都鍾意企喺道德高地<br />\n尤其英美嗰班高官議員<br />\n個個都將自己包裝成鋤強扶弱<br />\n勇武打到飛起 就算俾popo打死佢哋唔會同情<br />\n但有大班傷者求援 一講人道就啱哂佢哋胃口<br />\n呢啲喺佢哋國民眼中係做乜都會加分 佢哋點都會借機做啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">手足唔好淨係掛住打</span></strong><br />\n趁而家popo唔再強攻就要做返關公嘢<br />\n畫面背景最好係傷者訓哂喺地<br />\n前面坐住傷咗既手足發言<br />\n全部要卸gear 著返平民衫出鏡<br />\n<br />\n一場戰爭除咗示威 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲要係適當時機示弱</span></strong><br />\n<strong>搏同情 搶民心 無可否認勇武畫面係令到有班和理非冇行出嚟幫手</strong><br />\n希望poly入面有手足見到呢個post可以幫吓手去安排<br />\n救救大家!!<br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔到, 麻煩大家幫手推!!"},{"pid":"a5164d4e3993caf8132aa9bbec4f8e53fc265f46","tid":1735190,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3aa9d5f826d1d5f2797a5bc9b91bacc6446a00db","tid":1735190,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:29:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"175141f0c9e6b52169c8c84f2382fde0e5db0a75","tid":1735190,"uid":231853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:30:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b97d6d273233a0a22d75479b64be211bff77d36c","tid":1735190,"uid":200957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:32:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"87df80aa45e51c0397b93349be4377155707525b","tid":1735190,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:32:33.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<br />\n<br />\n唔該幫手推到入面手足睇到<br />\n<br />\n如果你有其他聯絡方法 麻煩forward俾佢哋睇"},{"pid":"ea69d7cb20a29ad5eaf8e301f2893c40061d4305","tid":1735190,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim